# Data Dictionary: Gold Layer

## Overview
The **Gold Layer** represents the refined, business-level data representation. It is structured using a **Star Schema** consisting of dimension and fact tables, optimized for analytical reporting and BI tool consumption.

---

## 1. gold.dim_customers
**Purpose:** Stores enriched customer information, including demographic and geographical data.

| Column Name | Data Type | Description |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **customer_key** | INT | Surrogate key uniquely identifying each customer record (Primary Key). |
| **customer_id** | INT | Unique identifier from the source system used for tracking. |
| **first_name** | NVARCHAR(50) | The customer's first name. |
| **last_name** | NVARCHAR(50) | The customer's last name. |
| **country** | NVARCHAR(50) | The customer's country of residence. |
| **marital_status** | NVARCHAR(50) | The customer's marital status. |
| **gender** | NVARCHAR(50) | The customer's gender (e.g., 'Male', 'Female', 'N/A'). |
| **birth_date** | DATE | The customer's date of birth. |
| **dwh_creation_date** | DATETIME | Timestamp when the record was created in the Data Warehouse. |

---

## 2. gold.dim_products
**Purpose:** Provides a comprehensive catalog of products and their attributes.

| Column Name | Data Type | Description |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **product_key** | INT | Surrogate key uniquely identifying each product (Primary Key). |
| **product_id** | INT | Unique identifier for internal tracking and referencing. |
| **product_number** | NVARCHAR(50) | Alphanumeric code used for categorization or inventory. |
| **product_name** | NVARCHAR(50) | Descriptive name of the product (includes type, color, size). |
| **category_id** | NVARCHAR(50) | Unique identifier for the highest level of product classification. |
| **subcategory** | NVARCHAR(50) | Detailed classification of the product within its category. |
| **maintenance** | NVARCHAR(50) | Indicates if the product requires check-ups (Yes/No). |
| **cost** | INT | The base cost or acquisition price of the product. |
| **product_line** | NVARCHAR(50) | The specific line the product belongs to (e.g., Road, Mountain). |
| **start_date** | DATE | The date when the product became available for sale. |

---

## 3. gold.fact_sales
**Purpose:** Stores transactional data and key metrics for sales performance.

| Column Name | Data Type | Description |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **order_number** | NVARCHAR(50) | Unique identifier for each sales transaction. |
| **product_key** | INT | Foreign key linking to `gold.dim_products`. |
| **customer_key** | INT | Foreign key linking to `gold.dim_customers`. |
| **order_date** | DATE | The date the order was placed. |
| **shipping_date** | DATE | The date the order was shipped. |
| **due_date** | DATE | The date when payment was due. |
| **sales_amount** | INT | Total monetary value of the transaction. |
| **quantity** | INT | Number of units sold. |
| **price** | INT | The unit price of the product. |
